snippet.title: Tom's Cruise Fast Walkthrough
snippet.description:
Play it here: http://snapbreak.com/puzzle/toms-cruise-3

Tom and Kimberly are having their honeymoon on the Queen Beatrice cruise ship, but after a long night of partying, Kimberly went missing. Do your best to help Tom find her.
